Package com.varukha.webproject.command

package com.varukha.webproject.command
This command package contains all required commands to execute by front-controller and utility classes: CommandName - contains names of commands. CommandFactory - contains commands to execute. Message - contains messages display on the interface. PagePath - contains all page paths and commands routs. ParameterAndAttribute - contains all parameters and attributes. Router - used to routing between application pages. Package imp where all commands are implemented.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Dmytro Varukha
  • Class
    Description
    Command
    Interface Command contain contracts of single execute method that used to execute application commands.
    CommandFactory
    Class CommandFactory contains all types of commands that using in application.
    CommandName
    Class CommandName contain names of commands from jsp pages that used to execute user's operations.
    Message
    Class Message contains all types of messages that using in the application in order to display on user interface.
    PagePath
    Class PagePath contain all page paths and commands routs that used in application commands.
    ParameterAndAttribute
    Class ParameterAndAttribute contain all parameters and attributes that used as a keys to set data from user request.

    Class Router used to routing between application pages.
